
  Vanilluxe    Ice Type Pokémon

  Swallowing large amounts of 
  water, they make snow clouds 
  inside their bodies and attack 
  their foes with violent blizzards. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Vanillite ► Vanillish ► Vanilluxe

